{"title_page": "33rd Golden Globe Awards", "text_new": "{{Infobox film awards\n| number = 33\n| award = Golden Globe Awards\n| image = \n| caption = \n| date = 24 January 1976\n| best_film_drama = '' One Flew Over the Cuckoo's Nest ''\n| best_film_musical_or_comedy = '' The Sunshine Boys ''\n| last = 32nd\n| next = 34th\n}}\nThe '''33rd [[Golden Globe Award]]s''', honoring the best in [[film]] and [[television]] for 1975, were held on January 24, 1976.\n\n==Winners and nominees==\n\n===Film===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width=100%\"\n! colspan=\"2\" |Best Motion Picture\n|-\n! style=\"width=50%\" |[[Golden Globe Award for Best Motion Picture \u2013 Drama|Drama]]\n! style=\"width=50%\" |[[Golden Globe Award for Best Motion Picture \u2013 Musical or Comedy|Comedy or Musical]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''''[[One Flew Over the Cuckoo's Nest (film)|One Flew Over the Cuckoo's Nest]]'''''\n**''[[Barry Lyndon]]''\n**''[[Dog Day Afternoon]]''\n**''[[Jaws (film)|Jaws]]''\n**''[[Nashville (film)|Nashville]]''\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''''[[The Sunshine Boys (1975 film)|The Sunshine Boys]]'''''\n**''[[Funny Lady]]''\n**''[[The Return of the Pink Panther]]''\n**''[[Shampoo (film)|Shampoo]]''\n**''[[Tommy (1975 film)|Tommy]]''\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" |Best Performance in a Motion Picture \u2013 Drama\n|-\n![[Golden Globe Award for Best Actor \u2013 Motion Picture Drama|Actor]]\n![[Golden Globe Award for Best Actress in a Motion Picture \u2013 Drama|Actress]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''[[Jack Nicholson]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[One Flew Over the Cuckoo's Nest (film)|One Flew Over the Cuckoo's Nest]]'' as [[Randle McMurphy]]'''\n**[[Gene Hackman]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[French Connection II]]'' as [[Jimmy \"Popeye\" Doyle|Det. Jimmy \"Popeye\" Doyle]]\n**[[Al Pacino]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[Dog Day Afternoon]]'' as [[John Wojtowicz|Sonny Wortzik]]\n**[[Maximilian Schell]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[The Man in the Glass Booth]]'' as Arthur Goldman\n**[[James Whitmore]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[Give 'em Hell, Harry!]]''