useau|Inspector Jacques Clouseau]]\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*''' [[Ann-Margret]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[Tommy (1975 film)|Tommy]]'' as Nora Walker'''\n**[[Julie Christie]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[Shampoo (film)|Shampoo]]'' as Jackie Shawn\n**[[Goldie Hawn]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[Shampoo (film)|Shampoo]]'' as Jill\n**[[Liza Minnelli]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[Lucky Lady]]'' as Claire\n**[[Barbra Streisand]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[Funny Lady]]'' as [[Fanny Brice]]\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" |Best Supporting Performance in a Motion Picture \u2013 Drama, Comedy or Musical\n|-\n![[Golden Globe Award for Best Supporting Actor \u2013 Motion Picture|Supporting Actor]]\n![[Golden Globe Award for Best Supporting Actress \u2013 Motion Picture|Supporting Actress]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*''' [[Richard Benjamin]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[The Sunshine Boys (1975 film)|The Sunshine Boys]]'' as Ben Clark'''\n**[[John Cazale]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[Dog Day Afternoon]]'' as [[Salvatore Naturale|Sal]]\n**[[Charles Durning]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[Dog Day Afternoon]]'' as Eugene Moretti\n**[[Henry Gibson]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[Nashville (film)|Nashville]]'' as Haven Hamilton\n**[[Burgess Meredith]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[The Day of the Locust]]'' as Harry Greener\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''[[Brenda Vaccaro]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[Jacqueline Susann's Once Is Not Enough (film)|Jacqueline Susann's Once Is Not Enough]]'' as Linda Riggs'''\n**[[Ronee Blakley]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[Nashville (film)|Nashville]]'' as Barbara Jean\n**[[Geraldine Chaplin]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[Nashville (film)|Nashville]]'' as Opal\n**[[Lee Grant]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[Shampoo (film)|Shampoo]]'' as Felicia Karpf\n**[[Barbara Harris (actress)|Barbara Harris]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[Nashville (film)|Nashville]]'' as Albuquerque\n**[[Lily Tomlin]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[Nashville (film)|Nashville]]'' as Linnea Reese\n|-\n! colspan=2 | Other\n|-\n![[Golden Globe Award for Best Director|Best Director]]\n![[Golden Globe Award for Best Screenplay|Best Screenplay]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*''' [[Milo\u0161 Forman]]&nbsp;\u2014 ''[[O